!!Floating Images
To clear a float, append...
{{{
@@clear:both;display:block; @@
}}}

!!Floating Left...
{{{
[<img[http://wikitext.tiddlyspace.com/fractalveg.jpg]]
@@clear:both;display:block; all clear@@
}}}
